sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>IncidentListPage
    participant API1 as DRF<br/>IncidentNotesListView
    participant API2 as DRF<br/>IncidentNoteCreateView
    participant SER as IncidentNoteSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Open incident detail, view notes tab
    FE->>API1: GET /api/incidents/{id}/notes/
    API1->>DB: IncidentNote.objects.filter(incident=id)
    DB-->>API1: QuerySet[IncidentNote]
    API1->>SER: IncidentNoteSerializer(notes, many=True)
    API1-->>FE: 200 OK {notes: [...]}
    FE-->>U: Display existing investigation notes
    U->>FE: Type note content, click "Add Note"
    FE->>API2: POST /api/incidents/{id}/notes/create/ {content: "..."}
    API2->>SER: IncidentNoteSerializer.validate(data)
    API2->>DB: IncidentNote.objects.create(incident, author=user, content)
    DB-->>API2: IncidentNote created
    API2-->>FE: 201 Created {note}
    FE-->>U: Note appended to investigation timeline
